title: VirtueMart & Joomla! - Setting Up A Domain & Hosting Account 1st
description:
VirtueMart & Joomla! - Setting Up A Domain & Hosting Account For A Fully Functional Store

Why pay HUNDREDS if not THOUSANDS of dollars to setup your very own online store and website when you can learn everything you need for just $19.99?
